This is the stable version of the libraries available from the coqtail project (rev 83).
Feel free to send us feedback or ideas on the coqtail-devml mailing-list.

** How-to build the libraries **
The Makefile should work : open a terminal and type "make"

** How-to use the libraries **
You can use coqide's "-I" option to add paths where it should search for coq modules


** The coqtail project links **
Website (with online coqdoc of the current stable version) : http://coqtail.sourceforge.net/
Sourceforge : http://sourceforge.net/projects/coqtail/
Wiki (doc) : http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/coqtail/
